                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Link Vitality can be equipped on Kubrows , Kavats , MOAs , and Hounds , but not on Sentinels ."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "source": "local-wiki-sqlite",
                  "pageTitle": "Link Vitality",
                  "pageId": 510639,
                  "revisionId": 2696078,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Link Vitality cannot be equipped simultaneously with Enhanced Vitality ."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "source": "local-wiki-sqlite",
                  "pageTitle": "Link Vitality",
                  "pageId": 510639,
                  "revisionId": 2696078,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Link Vitality uses the player's maximum health as the base, which means using Umbral Vitality with the full set bonus, Primed Vigor , Gladiator Resolve , Saxum Carapace , Jugulus Carapace , Carnis Carapace , and Physique (with Coaction Drift ) can further increase a companion's maximum health."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "source": "local-wiki-sqlite",
                  "pageTitle": "Link Vitality",
                  "pageId": 510639,
                  "revisionId": 2696078,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Health buffs from other sources, including Chroma 's Elemental Ward , Wisp 's Reservoirs , or Arcane Blessing also apply."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "source": "local-wiki-sqlite",
                  "pageTitle": "Link Vitality",
                  "pageId": 510639,
                  "revisionId": 2696078,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "With Link Vitality on a Sahasa Kubrow or Chesa Kubrow , a maximum health value of 17,784.105 can be achieved using the above health mods with an Inaros Prime ."
                }
              }
            ],
